[[File:Celto.jpg|200px|thumb|Celto]]
'''Celto''' was a small leafy green that could be included with various meals to enhance flavor. The chef [[Gormaanda/Legends|Gormaanda]] provided instructional [[Holovid/Legends|holovids]] including tips on how to properly use this food additive for various meals. Shortly after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Mallatobuck/Legends|Mallatobuck]] used liberal helpings of this item when preparing a special [[Life Day/Legends|Life Day]] ''Bantha Surprise '' dinner for her husband, [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]].

